<p>
Now that we have the '<%= link_to "mount", post_url("3D Printing Fun") %>' component of the PI Sw1tch, and an awesome way to playgames through the PI on our TV, we need a collection of games to play! It goes without saying that <%= link_to "Nethack", "http://thegreatestgameyouwilleverplay.com/" %> was installed (combined w/ ssh X11 forwarding = persistent graphical nethack anywhere = epicness!!!). But I also happen to have a huge box of Retro video games (dating back to my childhood), which would be good to load onto the device. But unfortunately cloning so many games would take some time, and there are already <%= link_to "online databases", "https://www.emuparadise.me/" %> of these backups, so I opted to write a small web app to download and manage the collection.
</p>

